PrecisFix the salary of LYNE GAUTHIER, a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montréal Regional Office), for the period she is acting as Assistant Deputy Chairperson, commencing on July 7, 2011, and until such time an Assistant Deputy Chairperson is designated or until the coming into force of the Balanced Refugee Reform Act, whichever is earlier.
